1. *Konji* su trčali po polju. (The *horses* were running in the field.)
2. Imam *konje* na farmi. (I have *horses* on my farm.)
3. Moji omiljeni *konjići* su bili u trci. (My favorite *ponies* were in the race.)
4. Volim da vozim *konja*. (I love to ride a *horse*.)
5. *Konjima* je potrebno puno pažnje i brige. (Horses require a lot of attention and care.)
6. Moja ćerka ima omiljenog *konjića* koji joj je najdraži plišani igračka. (My daughter has a favorite *little horse* that is her favorite stuffed toy.)
7. *Konjicima* je potrebna kvalitetna ishrana da bi bili zdravi i jaki. (Ponies require quality nutrition to be healthy and strong.)
8. Videli smo *konje* u prirodi dok smo se šetali. (We saw *horses* in the nature while we were walking.)
9. *Konjima* treba redovna veterinarska kontrola kako bi bili zdravi. (Horses need regular veterinary check-ups to be healthy.)
10. *Konje* često koriste u vojsci za prevoz tereta. (Horses are often used in the army for transportation of cargo.)